{"tid":1686178,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"法庭拒絕頒下無線電視申請禁制令","createTime":"2019-11-01T03:27:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T04:52:09.000Z","uid":322732,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"beb24eda59d3ce16f8326175b75e0f4ae1541713","tid":1686178,"uid":322732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T03:27:03.000Z","msg":"早前電視廣播有限公司向原訟庭申請臨時禁制令，禁止任何人士非法及故意襲擊無綫電視記者及毀壞他們的財物。<br />\n<br />\n法官表示，過去一個月針對無綫電視的事件已經無再出現，質疑法庭現階段是否有需要頒下相關禁制令。法官又質疑申請人如何確保公眾知悉禁制令內容，她說無綫在採訪示威活動時已遮蓋公司標誌，其記者亦不會表明所屬公司，一旦頒下禁制令，無綫一方是否要每次在示威現場都展示禁制令及表明身份。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1489459-20191101.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1489459-20191101.htm&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvKQBVxexyTzYM5wEVuQb9nQ%3D&h=2b7a52ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1489459-20191101.htm&h=780a2c14\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1489459-20191101.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n有左禁制令 cctvb咪要掛番個狗牌<br />\n貼埋張禁制令係部cam度 話比人知佢係cctvb<br />\n法庭係幫緊保護佢班前線記者咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ee8546e7039e5372475364a935d8000ba8fe24c","tid":1686178,"uid":15730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T04:52:09.000Z","msg":"個官都知都無人搞佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}